<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>餐饮 on 靖风行</title><link>https://blog.haohome.top/categories/%E9%A4%90%E9%A5%AE/</link><description>Recent content in 餐饮 on 靖风行</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 08 Jul 2022 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.haohome.top/categories/%E9%A4%90%E9%A5%AE/rss.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>预制菜行业背景</title><link>https://blog.haohome.top/post/food/%E9%A2%84%E5%88%B6%E8%8F%9C%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%9A%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90/</link><pubDate>Fri, 08 Jul 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.haohome.top/post/food/%E9%A2%84%E5%88%B6%E8%8F%9C%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%9A%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90/</guid><description>概念 广义上预制菜是指对农、畜、禽、水产品等原料进行前期处理后，配以各种辅料，经预加工（如分切、搅拌、腌制、滚揉、成型、调味）后所制的成品或半</description></item><item><title>餐饮研发员的基本素质</title><link>https://blog.haohome.top/post/food/%E9%A4%90%E9%A5%AE%E7%A0%94%E5%8F%91%E5%91%98%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E7%B4%A0%E8%B4%A8/</link><pubDate>Tue, 12 Jul 2016 22:04:11 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.haohome.top/post/food/%E9%A4%90%E9%A5%AE%E7%A0%94%E5%8F%91%E5%91%98%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E7%B4%A0%E8%B4%A8/</guid><description>&lt;p>餐饮属于快节奏的行业，对研发员的工作是很大的挑战。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>现在的餐饮都要做标准化，也要做创新，那么如何去做一位合格的餐饮研发员呢？&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>浅谈餐饮的标准化</title><link>https://blog.haohome.top/post/food/%E6%B5%85%E8%B0%88%E9%A4%90%E9%A5%AE%E7%9A%84%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E5%8C%96/</link><pubDate>Thu, 12 May 2016 20:25:06 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.haohome.top/post/food/%E6%B5%85%E8%B0%88%E9%A4%90%E9%A5%AE%E7%9A%84%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E5%8C%96/</guid><description>&lt;hr>
&lt;img src="https://blog.haohome.top/images/西红柿炒鸡蛋.jpg" width=50%>
&lt;p>对于餐饮，我其实第一感觉就是不喜欢，因为不规范。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>餐饮从业者大部分都是厨师，他们有丰富的厨艺和从业经验，可以说他们炒一个菜是分分钟的事。但是，并不是每一位厨师都是大师，更多的是一个厨子。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>苹果为什么会褐变</title><link>https://blog.haohome.top/post/food/%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E4%BC%9A%E8%A4%90%E5%8F%98/</link><pubDate>Tue, 19 Apr 2016 00:34:14 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.haohome.top/post/food/%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E4%BC%9A%E8%A4%90%E5%8F%98/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://blog.haohome.top/imgs/img-lazy-loading.gif" data-src="https://haohome.top/Apple-whole-fresh-and-brown.jpg" alt="image" />
当切开的苹果不及时吃掉，它就会由白色苹果慢慢变成暗淡的棕褐色苹果，影响你的食欲。最好的消息是它依然是安全的苹果，你可以吃掉它。导致苹果变色的原因是酶促褐变，当植物组织内存在的酶与多酚类物质结合在氧气的环境下产生的分子反应，产生的黑色素。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>一年四季的时令蔬菜水果表</title><link>https://blog.haohome.top/post/food/%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E5%9B%9B%E5%AD%A3%E7%9A%84%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%A4%E8%94%AC%E8%8F%9C%E6%B0%B4%E6%9E%9C%E8%A1%A8/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.haohome.top/post/food/%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E5%9B%9B%E5%AD%A3%E7%9A%84%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%A4%E8%94%AC%E8%8F%9C%E6%B0%B4%E6%9E%9C%E8%A1%A8/</guid><description>&lt;hr>
